  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK588">
<l>oṟṟoṟṟit tanta poruḷaiyu maṟṟumō </l>
<l>roṟṟiṉā loṟṟik koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let not a king receive the information which a spy has discovered and made known to him, until he has examined it by another spy.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
